headline: T. Rowe Price price target lowered to $89 from $95 at BofA
summary: BofA lowered the firm’s price target on T. Rowe Price (TROW) to $89 from $95 and keeps an Underperform rating on the shares. Over the last two weeks, five traditional asset managers reported monthly assets under management and, on average, December net flows declined month-over-month with one of the five generating positive flows for the month while four others reported net outflows, the analyst tells investors.
